        "body": "## Summary\n\n- Adds the Control UI Projects workspace implementation: durable project store, Gateway project RPC methods, project/session association, resource notes/uploads, archive/restore, and the Projects dashboard tab.\n- Adds the SNES Studio dashboard surface and core SNES artifact builder used by the dashboard smoke path.\n- Adds a unified `pnpm ui:smoke:dashboard` suite for Projects, SNES Studio, and safe SNES hardware-proof artifact generation, then wires it into CI, release checks, and Full Release Validation rerun groups.\n- Documents the dashboard smoke commands, SNES Studio page, and release artifacts.\n\n## Real behavior proof\n\n- **Behavior or issue addressed:** Dashboard Projects and SNES Studio are now implemented and covered by real Control UI smoke tests so CI/release can catch regressions in project persistence/archive/restore, SNES Studio browser create/edit/play/export, and safe SNES hardware-proof artifact generation.\n- **Real environment tested:** OpenClaw Mac Studio clean worktree at head `07050048264e12b4bfdcb65b2fef06e132ca62aa`, Playwright Chromium against loopback `127.0.0.1`, local Dashboard Gateway-backed Projects smoke, static SNES Studio route smoke, and artifact output under `.artifacts/dashboard-smoke-suite/2026-05-31T00-51-32-539Z`.\n- **Exact steps or command run after this patch:** `pnpm ui:smoke:dashboard -- --artifact-profile local`\n- **Evidence after fix:** Copied live output from the terminal capture after this patch is included here. Console output showed the final dashboard smoke summary returned `\"ok\": true` with all three suite steps exit 0: Projects dashboard smoke, SNES Studio dashboard smoke, and SNES Studio hardware proof bundle. Projects smoke opened `http://127.0.0.1:60518/projects`, reported `authUrlClean: true`, created `Projects Smoke 1780188696538`, added a note resource, archived it through the dashboard UI, restored it through Archived Projects, and recorded no console, response, or page errors. SNES Studio smoke opened `http://127.0.0.1:60562/snes-studio?__openclaw_skip_auto_agent_team=1`, captured screenshots at `.artifacts/dashboard-smoke-suite/2026-05-31T00-51-32-539Z/snes-studio-smoke/local/desktop-live-playtest.png`, `.artifacts/dashboard-smoke-suite/2026-05-31T00-51-32-539Z/snes-studio-smoke/local/desktop-guided-platformer.png`, and `.artifacts/dashboard-smoke-suite/2026-05-31T00-51-32-539Z/snes-studio-smoke/local/mobile-guided-platformer.png`, and downloaded `.sfc`, emulator-proof JSON, and proof-run script artifacts.\n- **Observed result after fix:** Projects final store verified `total: 1`, `active: 1`, `archived: 0`; SNES Studio verified one-prompt build, live playtest canvas, selected-area prompt edits, preview/download flow, mobile guided flow, and explicit external-proof blockers for unavailable physical FXPAK/SRAM evidence while keeping the safe artifact bundle non-blocking.\n- **What was not tested:** Physical FXPAK PRO copy and post-power-cycle SRAM after-image evidence were not tested because no mounted FXPAK/SD2SNES-style volume or after-power-cycle SRAM image was available; the smoke records those as explicit non-blocking blockers unless `--require-complete` is used.\n\n## Verification\n\n- `pnpm test src/projects/store.test.ts src/gateway/server-methods/projects.test.ts ui/src/ui/controllers/projects.test.ts ui/src/ui/views/projects.test.ts ui/src/ui/views/snes-studio.test.ts packages/snes-studio-core/src/index.test.ts test/scripts/control-ui-dashboard-smoke-suite.test.ts test/scripts/snes-studio-hardware-proof.test.ts test/scripts/control-ui-snes-studio-smoke.test.ts test/scripts/control-ui-smoke-url.test.ts test/scripts/openclaw-cross-os-release-checks.test.ts test/scripts/check-workflows.test.ts`\n- `pnpm tsgo:core && pnpm tsgo:test:src && pnpm tsgo:test:ui && pnpm tsgo:test:packages`\n- `pnpm build`\n- `pnpm check:docs`\n- `pnpm ui:build && pnpm ui:smoke:snes-studio`\n- `pnpm ui:smoke:dashboard -- --artifact-profile local`